<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 1px dashed #ccc;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .container img {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .delv-head {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .delv-h3,
      .delv-h4 {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #333;
        margin-top: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: normal;
      }

      .delv-desc {
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        text-align: justify;
      }

      .quote-info,
      .customer-info {
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .delv-speach {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: justify;
      }

      .delv-speach p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .delv-list {
        padding-left: 20px;
        color: #555;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .delv-list-item {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .delv-close,
      .delv-comp {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }

      .delv-comp {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img src="{{ logo_main }}" height="42" width="112" />
      <p class="delv-head">Current Job Updates</p>
      <hr style="border: 1px solid #ccc; margin-bottom: 20px" />

      {{ job_updates }}

      <hr
        style="border: 1px solid #ccc; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px"
      />

      <p class="delv-speach">
        Calling all folks in distress! It's time for the legendary Garrett, cape
        flowing and charm overflowing, to swoop in and save the day! Got pesky
        tasks that won't quit bugging you? Confused like a squirrel in a maze?
        Or just craving a good belly laugh? Look no further, 'cause I'm here to
        be your superhero! When you're feeling stuck or blue, just holler my
        name, and I'll be there faster than you can say'supercalifragilisticexpialidocious'!
         And hey, don't fret;So, let's shake off those worries, slap on a grin, and let the
        laughter flow! Garrett to the rescue - making your day brighter, one
        joke at a time!
      </p>
      <p class="delv-speach">üòâ Keep up the fantastic work!</p>
      <p class="delv-speach">Your friendly neighborhood Garrett ü¶∏‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è</p>
      <p class="delv-comp">{{ company_website }}</p>
      <p class="delv-comp">{{ info_email }}</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
